data.title: Alti Gulskogen shopping mall
data.meta_description: Alti Gulskogen is located in Drammen, and has 120 stores and 10 places to eat. We have 1100 parking spaces and 8 charging spots for electric cars.
data.text:
120 shops and over 10 places to eat, 1100 parking spaces - we are the leading shopping center in the region. You find us west of the inner city of Drammen. There is a train station close by, and a bus stop right next to the center (named "Gulskogen senter")

Hungry? Want a short break from your travels? Alti Gulskogen has many pleasant places for you to enjoy some food and drinks. We also offer take away. Welcome!
